Diamond::

She looked at him,"Why are you worried about it." She still didn't 
trust him. After all those years with the Council, she had learned to 
trust no one.  She still wasn't sure about her own safety here, but 
for the moment, she needed a place to stay and as long as they didn't 
try anything, she would stay.
